pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `GpsFilePoints` ( `UserID` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `FileID` int(5) NOT NULL, `PointID` int(7) NOT NULL, `Lat` double(12,9) NOT NULL, `Lon` double(12,9) NOT NULL, `Ele` float(7,2) NOT NULL, `Time` varchar(24) NOT NULL, `Course` float(9,6) NOT NULL, `Hdop` float(9,6) NOT NULL, `Sat` int(3) NOT NULL, `Filtered` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`UserID`,`Lat`,`Lon`,`Time`), KEY `Time` (`Time`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 COMMENT='Holds all GPS points associated with an uploaded file.';
